### Test Case ID: TC030
**Target Description**: Verify that banner does not appear when restaurant is open  
**Suite**: Ordering Time Restrictions  
**Type**: Functional  
**Priority**: High  
---

#### Pre-conditions:
1. The user is on any page of the website (e.g. Homepage: https://simply33food.com/en).  
2. Current system time: Friday 12:00 (restaurant is open).

---

#### Steps to Execute:

| Step | Action | Expected Result | Pass | Fail | Bug Report ID |
|------|--------|------------------|------|------|----------------|
| 1 | Observe the page after full load | No banner is displayed; user can interact freely with the website |      |      |                |
| 2 | Wait for 10+ seconds | No banner appears after 10 seconds or any additional time |      |      |                |

---

#### Notes:
- Working hours: Mo-Thu 16:00-0:00 | Fri 11:00-18:30 | Sat 19:00-2:00 | Sun 12:00-0:00

